      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's more than just feeling like a stranger though. it's like the spark, the actual life... it's just gone. like the real me is dead and buried and i'm just this hollow thing that's been dragging itself around for years. it feels so heavy. it feels pointless to keep pretending there's anyone actually home in here.",
